summary: AN ORDINANCE amending the Seattle City Employees' Retirement Code, SMC Chapter 4.36, to correct outdated references and practices; and amending sections 4.36.100, 4.36.103, 4.36.110, 4.36.124, 4.36.190, 4.36.191, 4.36.195, and 4.36.400; and repealing sections 4.36.191.5 and 4.36.197 of the Seattle Municipal Code.
